{"tid":775063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵：沉降未必越來越差 有些地方可因地下水位改變而回復？？/ 契弟鄭泳舜","createTime":"2018-08-10T23:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T06:39:01.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ad0526e8cd266c10eeaeb809b9dc2065711a8e52","tid":775063,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T23:06:59.000Z","msg":"港鐵常務總監(車務及中國內地業務)金澤培說：「停工不是因為覺得危險，我們是希望釋除公眾疑慮，給我們時間審視，確認所有數據及周邊設施是真正的安全。<span style=\"color: red;\">沉降未必越來越差，因為沉降有些地方，會如果地下水位改變而回復。</span>大家都知道灣仔北是一個填海地區，也有其他基建工程進行中，所以沉降有機會比較顯著。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5b6da885e60383de0732b6da/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5b6da885e60383de0732b6da%2F&d=0gxvhdtyQ%2Fmp1C1HbK9zhhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=141953bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5b6da885e60383de0732b6da/</a><br />\n<br />\n有得回復架咩？！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/065940_5206dc426ef91617bef89c299d651edb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F065940_5206dc426ef91617bef89c299d651edb.png&h=48eaf76e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5b6da8a8e60383de3832b6ce/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5b6da8a8e60383de3832b6ce%2F&d=0gxvhdtyQ%2Fmp1C1HbK9zhhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=7c6c128c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5b6da8a8e60383de3832b6ce/</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭生你土瓜灣站特權法調查投棄權，沙中線仲反對喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/13306/沙中線-特權法-田北辰-13306/毛孟靜動議特權法查土瓜灣站被否決-田北辰投贊成票：人生點都要有第一次\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F13306%2F%E6%B2%99%E